Quick-and-dirty guide to running the CPAN::Changes Kwalitee Service app:

NB: Currently, you will need to install CPAN::Mini::Visit from the svn 
repository: http://svn.ali.as/cpan/trunk/CPAN-Mini-Visit/

1. cpanm --installdeps .
2. minicpan
3. ./bin/deploy.pl
4. ./bin/indexer.pl -m /path/to/minicpan
5. ./bin/authors.pl -m /path/to/minicpan
6. ./bin/app.pl
